Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants where it appears
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - User when followed by Completed + Resolved compared to when followed by Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + In Call in cases where both activities occur consecutively
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + Resolved in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time of Accepted + Wait - User in variants containing multiple occurrences of Accepted + In Progress versus variants with a single occurrence
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + In Progress occurs

Name: Elapsed time between Queued + Awaiting Assignment and Accepted + Wait - User in variants that later include Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Cycle Time of Accepted + Wait - User when the case originates from resource groups in France versus Brazil or USA
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - User in variants that eventually lead to Completed + In Call
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants where it is immediately followed by Accepted + In Progress versus variants where it is followed directly by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that include Accepted + Wait - Implementation or Accepted + Wait - Vendor as alternative waiting states
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case
